cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper is about video object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also focuses on designing a light weight network architecture for mobile devices, which falls under the category of mobile computing (cs.MM). The proposed system is trained end-to-end, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the system involves object tracking across frames, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO).
